Nine teams are expected to battle it out for the Eastern Region Chapa Dimba football tournament to be held in 9th march in Kitui. Isiolo will play triumph from Embu, Super Solico are expected to face Moyale's samba boys while Malkia from Meru are expected to battle it out with Chuka in the ladies category. Marsabit Sakuu will also face St. Mary’s Ndovea in the ladies category.